How many Ways? can we apply css?
		   How to Apply	    Reusability
		   --------------------------------
1. Inline CSS      style - attr     No  (Tag level CSS)
2. Internal CSS    <style> Element  Yes (Page Level)
3. External CSS    <link>  Tag      Yes (Application LeveL)

